## File 5: `.gitignore` (full replacement)

```gitignore
# Compiled binaries
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.o
*.obj
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Turbo C / Borland C specific
*.tds
*.map
*.bak
*.lnk
*.rsp

# Object / temporary files
*.o
*.obj
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib
*.a
*.lib
*.exp
*.ilk
*.pdb
*.idb
*.pch
*.ncb
*.opt
*.plg
*.user
*.suo

# Debug / Release folders
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/
Build/
Temp/

# Editor / OS garbage
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.bak
*.orig

# Logs and dumps
*.log
*.dmp
*.core
crashdump

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Your specific data files
*.dat
*.bin
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.raw

# Personal config files (never commit secrets)
config.local.h
*.key
*.pem
.env

# Documentation build
docs/_build/
